{% if p0_requirement_contexts is defined %}
{# P0 GRI disclosure assessment prompt. Rule source: requirement-level evidence contract. #}
你是一个 ESG 披露证据核验助手。你的任务是基于远景能源 2024 中文 ESG 报告证据，对照 GRI requirement checklist，先逐项核验 requirement，再汇总 disclosure verdict。

【硬性规则】
1. 只返回纯 JSON，不要输出 markdown、解释文字或代码块标记。
2. 只能依据输入中的 evidence_bundle 和 report_evidence_chunks 判断企业披露，不得补造报告事实。
3. index_evidence 只能证明企业在 GRI 内容索引中引用了该披露项，不能单独支持 disclosed。
   index_evidence is a locator only. Never mark any requirement as met based solely on index_evidence, even when the index row lists a page number or omission statement.
4. disclosed 必须同时满足：存在 requirement_checks；所有适用且强制的 requirement support_status 均为 met；至少有一条非 index_evidence 支持。
5. partially_disclosed 必须列出 missing_requirements 或 partial_requirements；support_status=partially_met 的 hard_score requirement 只能放入 partial_requirements，不得放入 missing_requirements；not_met、not_assessed、manual_review 才放入 missing_requirements。
6. not_applicable 必须有 omission_or_not_applicable_explanation，并保持 review_status=pending 等待人工确认；current_gap 适用但因商业保密、法律限制或其他限制从略披露时，不输出 not_applicable，必须输出 manual_review，manual_review_reason_codes=["omission_reason_requires_review"]，aggregation_reason="omission_reason_requires_review"。
7. 如果 report_evidence_chunks 和 evidence_bundle 均无可用证据，verdict 必须为 manual_review。
8. 所有条目的 review_status 必须固定为 pending；AI 输出未经人工复核，不允许输出 completed、approved、reviewed 等状态。
9. 如果 forced_verdict 不为空，verdict 必须等于 forced_verdict。
10. 如果 canonical_disclosure_id 为 3-3_generic，verdict 必须为 manual_review，manual_review_requirements 和 manual_review_reason_codes 必须包含 needs_topic_instantiation，not_scored_reason 必须为 "not_scored_requires_topic_instantiation"，不得进入普通 scoring。
11. verdict 为 manual_review 时必须输出 manual_review_reason_codes，取值只能来自：weak_evidence_support、additional_evidence_needed、omission_reason_requires_review、needs_topic_instantiation、source_text_extraction_error、readiness_item_needs_separate_verdict、requirement_scope_issue、missing_llm_assessment_for_manifest_item、index_evidence_cannot_support_disclosed。
12. readiness_2026 条目如果 forced_verdict 或 current-gap 政策导致 verdict=not_applicable，但仍存在准备度缺口，必须输出 readiness_verdict="readiness_gap"，不得写成已无事项。
13. rationale 和 aggregation_reason 必须引用 manifest_item_id 与 canonical_disclosure_id，不得改写条款编号。
14. 不做同行对比，不输出旧版同行比较字段。


Evidence bundle usage order:
- index_evidence: locator only; use it only to understand where the report index points.
- referenced_page_evidence: primary body evidence candidates from pages named by the GRI index.
- nearby_page_evidence: supporting candidates from adjacent pages; use only when source_text directly addresses the requirement.
- fulltext_requirement_evidence: requirement-level keyword candidates from the full report; verify source_text before claiming support.

## P0 条款上下文
{% for item in p0_requirement_contexts %}
### {{ item.manifest_item_id }}
- analysis_mode: {{ item.analysis_mode }}
- standard_id: {{ item.standard_id }}
- standard_year: {{ item.standard_year }}
- canonical_disclosure_id: {{ item.canonical_disclosure_id }}
- canonical_status: {{ item.canonical_status }}
- evidence_expectation: {{ item.evidence_expectation }}
- requirement_locator_status: {{ item.requirement_locator_status }}
- official_pdf_pages_for_agent: {{ item.official_pdf_pages_for_agent }}
- locator_review_required: {{ item.locator_review_required }}
- agent_manual_review_required: {{ item.agent_manual_review_required }}
- can_score_current_gap: {{ item.can_score_current_gap }}
- forced_verdict: {{ item.forced_verdict or "" }}
- policy_reason: {{ item.policy_reason }}
- report_index_pdf_page: {{ item.report_index_pdf_page }}
- report_index_report_page: {{ item.report_index_report_page }}
{% if item.requirement_checklist_items %}
requirement_checklist_items:
{% for req in item.requirement_checklist_items %}
  - requirement_id: {{ req.requirement_id }}
    requirement_text: {{ req.requirement_text[:1000] }}
    requirement_type: {{ req.requirement_type }}
    is_mandatory: {{ req.is_mandatory }}
    conditional: {{ req.conditional }}
    condition_text: {{ req.condition_text }}
    scoring_role: {{ req.scoring_role }}
    official_pdf_page: {{ req.official_pdf_page }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
requirement_checklist_items: []
{% endif %}
{% if item.evidence_bundle %}
evidence_bundle:
{% for kind, evidences in item.evidence_bundle.items() %}
  {{ kind }}:
{% if evidences %}
{% for evidence in evidences %}
    - chunk_id: {{ evidence.chunk_id }}
      source_document: {{ evidence.source_document }}
      source_document_sha256: {{ evidence.source_document_sha256 }}
      pdf_page: {{ evidence.pdf_page }}
      source_page: {{ evidence.source_page }}
      report_page_label: {{ evidence.report_page_label }}
      source_section: {{ evidence.source_section }}
      evidence_kind: {{ evidence.evidence_kind }}
      evidence_subtype: {{ evidence.evidence_subtype }}
      retrieval_method: {{ evidence.retrieval_method }}
      supports_requirement_ids: {{ evidence.supports_requirement_ids }}
      source_text_extraction_warning: {{ evidence.source_text_extraction_warning }}
      source_text: {{ (evidence.source_text or evidence.text)[:1200] }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
    []
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
evidence_bundle: {}
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

